{"title":"Effetto Mariposa updates Caffélatex Tubeless Valves, adds wide Shelter frame protection","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/02/08/effetto-mariposa-updates-caffelatex-tubeless-valves-adds-wide-shelter-frame-protection/","date":1612811366000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>Effetto Mariposa has tweaked their Caffélatex tubeless valves &amp; Shelter Wide frame protection tape to help give your bike a winter refresh. The valves themselves get updated to better fit on more tubeless setups, with a new stealth look option &amp; integrated valve core remover. And the three levels of stick-on Shelter protection now better fit modern carbon frames.</p><h2>Effetto Mariposa updated Caffelatex Tubeless Valves</h2><figure id=\"attachment_251132\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-251132\"><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_silver-and-red.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_silver-and-red.jpg\" alt=\"Effetto Mariposa updated Caffelatex Tubeless Valves\" width=\"2000\" height=\"750\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_silver-and-red.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_silver-and-red.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_silver-and-red-297x111.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/E