a-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_silver-and-red-768x288.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_silver-and-red-1536x576.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_silver-and-red-696x261.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_silver-and-red-1068x401.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_silver-and-red-1920x720.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_silver-and-red-1120x420.jpg 1120w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-251132\">c. Effetto Mariposa</figcaption></figure><p>Mariposa’s latest Caffelatex Tubeless Valves aren’t exceptionally revolutionary, but rather <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2019/12/11/mariposa-adds-tappabuco-tubeless-tire-repair-cx-gravel-tyreinvader-protective-tape-more/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">update the originals</a>, bringing together a few key features we’ve seen before. Long aero-road friendly lengths, modular rubber bases to fit more rim profiles, and a functional cap with built-in valve core remover.</p><p>Together as one, they could be the exact setup you need, especially if you ride deep carbon tubeless wheels.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_tech-details.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_tech-details.jpg\" alt=\"Effetto Mariposa updated Caffelatex Tubeless Valves tech details &amp; fit\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_tech-details.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_tech-details.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_tech-details-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_tech-details-800x450.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_tech-details-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_tech-details-768x432.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_tech-details-696x392.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_tech-details-1068x601.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_tech-details-747x420.jpg 747w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_tech-details.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_tech-details-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_tech-details-800x450.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_tech-details-120x68.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_tech-details-768x432.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_tech-details-696x392.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_tech-details-1068x601.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_tech-details-747x420.jpg 747w\"></a>Three lengths of the alloy valves are available – 40mm, 70mm &amp; 100mm – with only the top 30mm getting threads. A molded-on rubber base forms a solid seal against rim bed with a mostly flat middle channel, or you can slide on the conical rubber washer for more curved rims. Unlike some similar valves that rely on alloy base &amp; thin washers, this setup looks less likely to deform when tightened down.</p><p>The cap with the integrated valve core remover is pretty much identical to the one we’ve used on Granite’s <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2019/04/09/granite-stash-es-chain-tool-in-a-bar-juicy-nipple-on-a-valve-funn-damental-pedals/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Juicy Nipples</a>, similar to <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/02/28/peatys-x-chris-king-tubeless-valves-are-a-match-made-in-anodization-heaven/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Peaty’s</a>. In my experience, this style fit doesn’t tend to be perfect. But I appreciate a functional cap, and it’s much more convenient than hunting down one of the little plastic valve tools.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_40mm-70mm-100mm-black-or-silver-with-red.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_40mm-70mm-100mm-black-or-silver-with-red.jpg\" alt=\"Effetto Mariposa updated Caffelatex Tubeless Valves sizes\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1000\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_40mm-70mm-100mm-black-or-silver-with-red.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_40mm-70mm-100mm-black-or-silver-with-red.jpg 1800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_40mm-70mm-100mm-black-or-silver-with-red-297x165.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_40mm-70mm-100mm-black-or-silver-with-red-800x444.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_40mm-70mm-100mm-black-or-silver-with-red-120x67.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_40mm-70mm-100mm-black-or-silver-with-red-768x427.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/