ex-Tubeless-Valves_40mm-70mm-100mm-black-or-silver-with-red-696x387.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_40mm-70mm-100mm-black-or-silver-with-red-1068x593.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Caffelatex-Tubeless-Valves_40mm-70mm-100mm-black-or-silver-with-red-756x420.jpg 756w\"></a></p><p>Effetto Mariposa has always sold their tubeless valves in silver with red caps, but now adds an all-black option for those who don’t feel so flashy. The valves sell in pairs for 16€ in the short 40mm, 28€ for medium 70mm, and 34€ for long 100mm.</p><h3>Effetto Mariposa Shelter Wide frame protection tape</h3><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_downtube.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_downtube.jpg\" alt=\"Effetto Mariposa Shelter Wide frame protection tape, downtube\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_downtube.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_downtube.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_downtube-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_downtube-800x600.