-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_downtube-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_downtube-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_downtube-1068x801.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_downtube-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_downtube-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_downtube-265x198.jpg 265w\"></a>Shelter Wide frame protection tape is also <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2019/12/11/mariposa-adds-tappabuco-tubeless-tire-repair-cx-gravel-tyreinvader-protective-tape-more/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">an update</a> to a long-running Mariposa product. Available in three thicknesses – 0.2mm ZeroDue, 0.6mm&nbsp;Road, and 1.2mm Off-Road – Effetto Mariposa’s Shelter tape is a clear, self-adhesive protective layer… essentially an anti-scratch sticker to keep your frame or components looking new longer.</p><figure id=\"attachment_251128\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-251128\"><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_1m-rolls-58mm-standard_80mm-wide.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_1m-rolls-58mm-standard_80mm-wide.jpg\" alt=\"Effetto Mariposa Shelter Wide frame protection tape, 58mm standard or 80mm wide\" width=\"2000