me-protection-tape_1m-rolls-58mm-standard_80mm-wide-1920x960.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_1m-rolls-58mm-standard_80mm-wide-840x420.jpg 840w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_1m-rolls-58mm-standard_80mm-wide.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_1m-rolls-58mm-standard_80mm-wide-297x149.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_1m-rolls-58mm-standard_80mm-wide-800x400.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_1m-rolls-58mm-standard_80mm-wide-120x60.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_1m-rolls-58mm-standard_80mm-wide-768x384.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_1m-rolls-58mm-standard_80mm-wide-1536x768.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_1m-rolls-58mm-standard_80mm-wide-696x348.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_1m-rolls-58mm-standard_80mm-wide-1068x534.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_1m-rolls-58mm-standard_80mm-wide-1920x960.jpg 1920w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_1m-rolls-58mm-standard_80mm-wide-840x420.jpg 840w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-251128\">58mm standard (left) or new 80mm Wide (right)</figcaption></figure><p>Sold in kits or rolls, many cyclists prefer the 1m &amp; 5m rolls that let you customize how you cover parts of your paintjob you are looking to protect.<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-4\"></span></p><p>But as Mariposa realized, modern carbon bike frame tubes and especially e-bikes keep getting so much bigger, that the standard 58mm rolls didn’t offer enough coverage. Now, Shelter Wide stretches that coverage up to 80mm wide.</p><p><a href=\"https://bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_Off-Road-thick-chainstay.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_Off-Road-thick-chainstay.jpg\" alt=\"Effetto Mariposa Shelter Wide frame protection tape, chainstay\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_Off-Road-thick-chainstay.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_Off-Road-thick-chainstay.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Effetto-Mariposa-Shelter-Wide-frame-protection-tape_Off-Road-thick-chainstay-297x167.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/bikerumor-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/